%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6619072e1caec1275a6f68b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMu%C3%B1oz%20wondered%20if%20he'd%20isolate%20himself%20from%20his%20network%20by%20moving%20to%20Chicago.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jaime%20Mu%C3%B1oz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20always%20played%20it%20safe%20and%20thought%20about%20security%20when%20it%20came%20to%20jobs.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20the%20first%20in%20my%20family%20to%20be%20well-off.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20worry%20about%20retirement%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20provide%20for%20my%20future%20kids%20and%20pass%20down%20the%20wealth%20that%20I%20accumulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20some%20research%20on%20how%20some%20of%20the%20richest%20people%20built%20their%20wealth.%20Many%20of%20them%20mentioned%20getting%20in%20early%20at%20a%20company%2C%20being%20one%20of%20the%20first%20employees%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-company-equity-works-in-startups-tech-jobs-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaving%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20offered%20another%20role%20as%20a%20senior%20strategy%20consultant%20with%20Accenture%2C%20based%20out%20of%20the%20San%20Francisco%20office.%20The%20offer%20included%20the%20option%20to%20buy%20shares%20of%20their%20stock%2C%20but%20I%20preferred%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20shares%20allocated%20to%20me%20at%20an%20early-stage%20startup.%20Bridge%20Money%20offered%20me%20the%20possibility%20of%20an%20equity%20grant%20%E2%80%94%20if%20all%20went%20well%20at%20the%20company%2C%20my%20equity%20would%20increase%20in%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20I%20would%20be%20a%20speck%20of%20dust%20in%20a%20huge%20company%20at%20Accenture.%20I'd%20already%20worked%20there%20from%202015%20to%202020%20as%20a%20strategy%20analyst%20and%20senior%20strategy%20consultant.%20There%20were%20multiple%20levels%20of%20seniority%20above%20