20struggle%20to%20handle%20phone%20orders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20voice%20AI%20service%20means%20diners%20can%20place%20delivery%20orders%20with%20services%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-history-milestones-food-delivery-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-make-money-uber-eats-doordash-driving-delivery-tips-college-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber%20Eats%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20having%20to%20order%20on%20an%20app%20or%20website%2C%20customers%20calling%20restaurants%20that%20use%20a%20product%20developed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkea-tech-startup-tapped-by-dominos-to-automate-phone-ordering-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20voice%20AI%20company%2C%20can%20simply%20say%20what%20they%20want%20to%20order.%20Kea%20then%20sends%20their%20order%20to%20a%20delivery%20aggregator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20much%20better%20and%20easier%20to%20just%20say%20something%20and%20have%20it%20done%20versus%20let%20me%20download%20an%20app%2C%20let%20me%20add%20everything%20to%20the%20cart%2C%20let%20me%20customize%20it%2C%20let%20me%20add%20my%20credit%20card%20to%20it%2C%20and%20then%20press%20all%20those%20buttons%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%20Ahmad%2C%20Kea's%20CEO%20and%20founder%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20app%20revolution%2C%20restaurants%20relied%20on%20phone%20calls%20for%20delivery%20orders.%20In%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.dominos.com%2Fstatic-files%2Fd91871d8-3c13-439f-bc86-b1efe79373d6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2085%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Domino's%20US%20sales%20were%20made%20digitally.%20But%20there%20are%20still%20use%20cases%20for%20ordering%20by%20phone%20rather%20than%20using%20a%20website%20or%20app%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20maybe%20driving%20the%20kids%20back%20from%20school%20and%20it%20just%20makes%20sense%20to%20hit%20that%20call%20button%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B30-second%20interaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20customers%20call%20to%20order%20delivery%20from%20a%20restaurant%20that%20uses%20Kea's%20service%2C%20they'll%20be%20linked%20to%20the%20voice%20AI%2C%20which%20restaurants%20can%20choose%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20accents.%20The%20AI%20guides%20them%20through%20the%20transactions%2C%20including%20suggesting%20add-ons%20and%20recommending%20items%20they%20got%20in%20previous%20orders%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20hear%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20software%20works%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkea.ai%2Fhow-it-works%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKea's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20Siri%20or%20Alexa%20where%20it's%20kind%20of%20stopping%20you%20and%20making%20you%20repeat%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20fluid%20in%20its%20interaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20the%20AI%20has%20problems%20understanding%20the%20customer%20%E2%80%93%20or%20vice%20versa%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20be%20transferred%20to%20a%20Kea%20human%20agent%20who'll%20complete%20the%20order%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%20About%20a%20quarter%20of%20calls%20made%20to%20Kea%20are%20transferred%20to%20its%20human%20agents%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKea%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20had%20agents%20in%20nine%20countries%20but%20that%20the%20majority%20were%20based%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKea%20uses%20an%20algorithm%20developed%20by%20Olo%20to%20determine%20which%20delivery%20services%20are%20available%20nearby%20and%20choose%20the%20best%20one%20for%20each%20customer%20based%20on%20the%20cost%20and%20estimated%20time%20of%20arrival%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%20The%20delivery%20platforms%20that%20Kea%20can%20refer%20orders%20to%20are%20DoorDash%2C%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20Postmates%2C%20Grubhub%2C%20and%20Favor%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20upsell%20them%20throughout%20the%20call%20and%20then%20at%20the%20very%20end%20of%20the%20call%2C%20they%20have%20the%20option%20to%20leave%20a%20tip%20for%20the%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmad%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20at%20that%20time%2C%20an%20ETA%20is%20provided%20to%20them%20and%20the%20order%20gets%20placed%20directly%20into%20the%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20don't%20need%20to%20have%20the%20delivery%20provider's%20app%20to%20use%20Kea's%20service%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%20They'd%20still%20be%20sent%20a%20link%20to%20track%20their%20driver%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20delivery%20provider%20%E2%80%93%20we're%20sort%20of%20just%20processing%20the%20voice%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhmad%20incorporated%20Kea%20back%20in%202018%2C%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20this%20whole%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-jpmorgan-ai-extraordinary-consequences-transformative-internet-electricity-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20model%20craze%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20new%20delivery-service%20tie-in%20aside%2C%20Kea%20has%20operated%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bcashier%20in%20the%20cloud%26quot%3B%20service%20for%20years%2C%20which%20takes%20pickup%20orders%20and%20answers%20basic%20questions%20like%20opening%20hours%20when%20customers%20ring%20restaurants%2C%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKea%20said%20that%20the%20pizza%20chains%20it%20worked%20with%20%E2%80%94%20which%20it%20said%20it%20couldn't%20name%20due%20to%20NDAs%20%E2%80%94%20were%20already%20using%20the%20AI%20delivery%20function.%20It%20plans%20to%20offer%20the%20service%20to%20its%20other%20restaurants%20later%20this%20month%2C%20it%20said.%20Kea%20takes%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20orders%20it%20takes%20for%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChains%20that%20Kea%20works%20with%20include%20Wayback%20Burger%2C%20Newk's%20Eatery%2C%20and%20California%20Fish%20Grill.%20Kea%20declined%20to%20say%20how%20many%20restaurants%20it%20operated%20in%2C%20but%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20hundreds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20them%20are%20high%20volume%20takeout%20places%2C%20pizza%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmad%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20folks%20that%20have%20three%20to%20five%20phone%20lines%20at%20their%20restaurants%20and%20they%20simply%20cannot%20answer%20all%20the%20calls%20at%20once.%20It's%20just%20way%20too%20cumbersome.%20And%20so%20we're%20really%20focusing%20on%20those%20brands%20first%2C%20the%20ones%20that%20just%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20incoming%20phone%20traffic%20and%20ultimately%20helping%20them%20with%20answering%20every%20single%20phone%20call%20versus%20putting%20people%20on%20hold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-voice-technology-doordash-uber-eats-orders-phone-call-delivery-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712917437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6617f05916bde8d4ead7ce83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-voice-technology-doordash-uber-eats-orders-phone-call-delivery-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Voice%20AI%20company%20Kea%20takes%20customers'%20orders%20in%20phone%20calls%20and%20sends%20them%20to%20delivery%20aggregators.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-voice-technology-doordash-uber-eats-orders-phone-call-delivery-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BMCM%20mints%20only%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20in%20South%20languages%