holds%20on%20the%20holidays%20compared%20to%20the%20NFL%2C%20and%20the%20gap%20is%20widening.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20five%20NBA%20games%20played%20on%20Christmas%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eaveraged%202.9%20million%20viewers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Ftv%2Ftv-news%2Fnfl-new-years-eve-holiday-2023-24-tv-ratings-1235780558%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20was%20down%2030%25%20from%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20NFL%20won't%20stop%20at%20Christmas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20NFL%20breaking%20from%20the%20tradition%20of%20avoiding%20Tuesday%20and%20Wednesday%20games%2C%20it%20not%20only%20could%20mean%20games%20on%20Christmas%20every%20year%2C%20but%20it%20could%20also%20be%20the%20first%20step%20in%20leading%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcsports.com%2Fnfl%2Fprofootballtalk%2Frumor-mill%2Fnews%2Fnfl-seems-to-be-moving-toward-tuesdays-and-wednesdays-and-maybe-fridays-and-saturdays%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20mid-week%20games%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20mid-week%20national%20TV%20games%20were%20an%20idea%20the%20league%20seemed%20to%20start%20warming%20up%20to%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20NFL%20Commissioner%20Roger%20Goodell%20told%20the%20media%20that%20short-week%20games%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcsports.com%2Fnfl%2Fprofootballtalk%2Frumor-mill%2Fnews%2Fnfl-seems-to-be-moving-toward-tuesdays-and-wednesdays-and-maybe-fridays-and-saturdays%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edo%20not%20lead%20to%20more%20injuries%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20referenced%20the%20league's%20success%20in%20moving%20games%20to%20non-traditional%20days%20due%20to%20COVID-19%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoutbreaks%20on%20teams%20in%202020%2C%20including%20one%20game%20that%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20instinct%20meshes%20with%20what%20Roger%20Goodell%20said%20when%20he%20invo