%20So%2C%20my%20favourite%20thing%20is%20to%20pick%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20what%20is%20growing%20in%20the%20garden.%20Locally%2C%20they%20grow%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(black%20gram)%20and%20make%20little%20dried%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(vegetable%20nuggets)%20out%20of%20it%20for%20winter%2C%20because%20nothing%20grows%20here%20in%20the%20cold%20weather.%20So%2C%20they%20dry%20whatever%20they%20grow%20in%20summer%20or%20make%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20keep%20them.%20I%20love%20serving%20my%20guests%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20zucchini-based%20dishes%20because%20it%20grows%20here%20in%20abundance.%20We%20prepare%20it%20in%20various%20ways.%20There%20are%20also%20local%20dishes%20like%20%3Cem%3Esiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20like%20a%20bao%20stuffed%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20also%20uses%20fiddlehead%20fern%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248547%2Fhomemade-pickles-athey-nallatha-hafez-rahman-akshay-raveendran-kerala-homemakers-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20pickles%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealong%20with%20other%20produce%20like%20persimmon%20%3Cem%3Eachar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20plum%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20peach%20jam%2C%20and%20quince%20jam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20homestay%20steeped%20in%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20is%20the%20one%20who%20handles%20all%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejugaads%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(an%20innovative%20way%20of%20problem-solving)%20as%20Shalini%20puts%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20informs%20that%20the%20homestay%20was%20made%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20it%20does%20not%20disturb%20the%20nature%20around.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20implemented%20a%20lot%20of%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20practices%