s%20are%20light%20enough%20to%20float%20on%20water%20and%20insulate%20the%20entire%20building.%20Furthermore%2C%20all%20windows%20are%20double-glazed%20with%20argon%20gas%20in%20between%20for%20additional%20insulation%2C%20and%20the%20roofs%20are%20insulated%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20heating%2C%20the%20property%20utilises%20geothermal%20heat%20pumps%2C%20tapping%20into%20a%20spring%20on%20the%20property%20for%20ground%20source%20water.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20water%2C%20naturally%20warm%20in%20winter%2C%20is%20cycled%20through%20the%20geothermal%20heat%20pump%20to%20extract%20heat%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20to%20heat%20the%20building.%20Underfloor%20pipes%2C%20spanning%20almost%20a%20kilometre%2C%20distribute%20this%20heat%20throughout%20the%20building%2C%20providing%20an%20efficient%20heating%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitin%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20faced%20several%20power%20cuts%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20be%20more%20sustainable%20and%20go%20solar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20run%20our%20operations%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power.%20We%20have%20a%20solar%20system%20in%20place%20that%20generates%20electricity%2C%20and%20our%20entire%20house%20runs%20on%20this.%20Even%20on%20days%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20as%20little%20as%2030%25%20sunlight%2C%20the%20system%20works%20efficiently.%20Additionally%2C%20any%20excess%20energy%20generated%20during%20the%20day%20is%20stored%20in%20batteries%2C%20which%20we%20then%20use%20for%20power%20backup%20when%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20six%20years%20of%20operations%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20hosted%20countless%20number%20of%20happy%20guests%20so%20far.%20Among%20them%20is%20Mumbai-based%20Priyanka%20who%20stayed%20at%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLocated%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Beas%20River%2C%20Shalini%20and%20Nitin%E2%80%99s%20homestay%20exceeded%20all%20our%20expectations.%20Surrounded%20by%20beautifu