3%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-8-1711367979-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-8-1711367979-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-8-1711367979-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-8-1711367979-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345733%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20snow%20leopard%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98ghost%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99%20for%20its%20natural%20camouflage%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Namgail%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetaliatory%20killings%20have%20always%20been%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction%20to%20snow%20leopards%20mauling%20the%20locals%E2%80%99%20livestock.%20And%20Namgail%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20where%20the%20conservancy%20steps%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20alongside%20the%20ferocious%20predator%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20dream%20for%20the%20pastoral%20communities%20of%20Ladakh.%20However%2C%20being%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F96401%2Fproject-shen-snow-leopard-conservation-women-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaintain%20their%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20money%20they%20earn%20through%20protecting%20it%20serves%20as%20an%20incentive.%20In%20fact%2C%20once%20hailed%20as%20pests%2C%20Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20now%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERi%20Gyancha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20this%20nickname%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20soften%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20snow%20leopard%20towards%20the%20locals%20who%20continue%20to%20see%20rare%20cases%20