2%3Esilica%20sand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20huge%20quartzite%20stones%20are%20broken%20and%20milled%2C%20dust%20is%20released.%20This%20dust%20contains%20silicon%20dioxide%20which%20when%20inhaled%20over%20some%20time%20leads%20to%20silicosis%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20noticing%20that%20our%20mother%20would%20cough%20a%20lot%20and%20often%20complained%20about%20facing%20difficulty%20in%20breathing.%20Day%20by%20day%2C%20she%20also%20started%20losing%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20four%20years%20until%20one%20day%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%20April%202012.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20we%20heard%20about%20the%20disease.%20We%20took%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20we%20were%20too%20young%20to%20understand%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20disease%20and%20how%20long%20she%20was%20going%20to%20stay%20with%20us.%20I%20was%2014%20years%20old%20then%2C%20and%20I%20was%20told%20that%20she%20would%20be%20home%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parvati%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%202012.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20succumbed%20to%20the%20disease.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe