uring%20that%20everyone%20with%20hearing%20loss%20can%20find%20a%20non-surgical%20alternative%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kanishka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20WHO%20estimating%20that%20one%20in%2010%20people%20will%20have%20disabling%20hearing%20loss%20by%202050%2C%20such%20solutions%20are%20definitely%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20WeHear%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Fdeafness-and-hearing-loss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWHO%20Report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712587714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kanishka%20Patel%20and%20Raj%20Shah%20co-founded%20WeHear%20to%20develop%20non-surgical%20solutions%20for%20people%20with%20hearing%20loss.%20HearNU%2C%20their%20bone%20conduction%20hearing%20aid%2C%20has%20sold%20over%2011%2C500%20units%2C%20earning%20revenue%20of%20Rs%205.5%20crore.%20They%20also%20secured%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Residents%20Can%20Do%20a%20Lot%20More%20to%20Save%20The%20City%E2%80%99s%20Water%20%26amp%3B%20It%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20Too%20Late%20to%20Start%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(In%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346640%2Fbengaluru-water-scarcity-crisis-solution