nt%20plant)%2C%20Vishwanath%20believes%20that%20if%20they%20make%20sure%20that%20their%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants%20are%20running%20well%2C%20then%20they%20can%20fulfil%20all%20their%20non-potable%20water%20requirements%20from%20those%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20residents%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%20well%2C%20their%20borewells%20will%20have%20water.%20If%20the%20community%20works%20around%20the%20lakes%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20comes%20together%2C%20and%20makes%20sure%20that%20the%20lake%20is%20cleaned%20up%20and%20de-silted%20along%20with%20the%20State%2C%20then%20these%20water%20bodies%20will%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20excess%20water%20from%20their%20STPs%20that%20are%20well%20treated%20can%20be%20led%20into%20these%20lakes%20so%20that%20it%20recharges%20the%20aquifers.%20I%20believe%20these%20are%20all%20the%20steps%20that%20citizens%20have%20to%20take%20to%20protect%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20water%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20what%20steps%20has%20he%20taken%20in%20his%20own%20home%20to%20reduce%20water%20consumption%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20being%20mindful%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20you%20consume%2C%20you%20can%20deploy%20technologies%20like%20aerators%20on%20your%20taps%20or%20shower%20heads.%20You%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20water%20you%20collect%20after%20cleaning%20your%20dishes%20is%20used%20to%20water%20your%20plants%20or%20the%20garden%20that%20you%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20case%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20all%20the%20greywater%20is%20recycled.%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20collect%20the%20wastewater%20from%20my%20washing%20machine%20and%20half-bucket%20bath%20water.%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F230971%2Fnagaland-small-biz-entrepreneur-woman-organic-soaps-oils-skincare-personal-care-eco-friendly-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20soaps%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20detergents%20which%20do%20not%20have%20phosphates%20and%20phthalates.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20wastewater%20from%20bathing%20or%20washing%20clothes%20can%20be%20used%20for%20swabbing%20the%20floor%2C%20watering%20the%20terrace%20garden%2C%20and%20cleaning%20the%20car.%20I%20have%20a%20dry%20compost%20toilet%20which%20requires%20no%20water%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20may%20seem%20a%20bit%20extreme%20to%20some%20but%20it%20has%20worked%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%E2%80%99s%20home%20also%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F92434%2Fa-r-shivakumar-rainwater-harvesting-bengaluru-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainwater%20harvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20that%20are%20operating%20optimally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20the%20last%20rains%20in%20the%20city%20were%20in%20November%2C%20our%201%2C000-litre%20rain%20barrel%20still%20has%20enough%20water%20for%20our%20drinking%20and%20cooking%20needs%20till%20June.%20I%20have%20taken%20away%20plants%20which%20would%20have%20otherwise%20grown%20and%20left%20the%20garden%20to%20be%20dry%20so%20that%20when%20the%20rains%20come%2C%20I%20can%20restart%20my%20garden.%20Right%20now%2C%20I%20only%20have%20drought-tolerant%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20use%20less%20energy%20(electricity).%20The%20less%20energy%20I%20use%2C%20the%20more%20water%20you%E2%80%99re%20saving%20in%20some%20dam%20or%20thermal%20power%20plant.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20the%20energy%20you%20use%20and%20about%20the%20food%20you%20eat%20so%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20waste%20it.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20steps%20I%20have%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FyyRNm-mFn7g%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FyyRNm-mFn7g%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98How%20can%20I%20reduce%20my%20water%20consumption%20by%2050%25%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20points%20mentioned%20by%20Vishwanath%20in%20reducing%20his%20water%20consumption%20was%20the%20use%20of%20aerators.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20simplest%20hacks%20you%20can%20adopt%20in%20your%20home%20to%20reduce%20water%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20Shashidhara%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20EverythingECO%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20startup%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20of%20water%20and%20waste%20management.%20Among%20the%20products%20EverythingECO%20manufactures%20are%20aerators%20that%20you%20can%20attach%20to%20washroom%20or%20kitchen%20taps%20and%20restrictors%20for%20shower%20heads%20and%20health%20faucets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKarunaprasada%20Kanavi%20and%20I%20started%20EverythingECO%20with%20a%20vision%20in%202016%20to%20bring%20sustainability%20to%20businesses%20and%20homes%2C%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20of%20water%20and%20waste%20management.%20Before%20getting%20into%20business%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20how%20people%20and%20different%20businesses%20were%20using%20water%2C%20what%20their%20daily%20consumption%20levels%20were%2C%20and%20started%20thinking%20of%20customised%20solutions%20required%20for%20each%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Save%20water%20in%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346781%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashidhara%20Kumaraswamy%20%26amp%3B%20Karunaprasada%20Kanavi%2C%20co-founders%20of%20EverythingEco.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shashidhara%20and%20his%20co-founder%20did%20a%20detailed%20audit%20on%20water%20consumption%20levels%20across%20multiple%20locations%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20they%20found%20that%20each%20business%20or%20residential%20unit%20has%20specific%20requirements%20based%20on%20its%20usage%20pattern.%20In%20certain%20locations%2C%20they%20found%20the%20flow%20rate%20measured%20in%20hand%20washing%20taps%20to%20be%20around%2015%20to%2016%20litres%20per%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%2C%20we%20have%20observed%20that%20when%20you%20buy%20taps%20of%20standard%20fittings%2C%20their%20flow%20rate%20is%20between%2014%20to%2018%20litres%20per%20minute%20based%20on%20water%20pressure.%20Most%20fixtures%20sold%20commercially%20do%20not%20have%20any%20aerators.%20They%20come%20with%20filters%20to%20filter%20out%20the%20dust.%20These%20filters%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20the%20job%20of%20water%20conservation%2C%20but%20only%20ensure%20the%20laminar%20flow%20of%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuring%20this%20audit%2C%20they%20concluded%20that%20taps%20for%20hand%20washing%20should%20never%20have%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%20more%20than%203%20litres%20per%20minute.%20Similarly%2C%20for%20kitchens%2C%20they%20understood%20that%20people%20required%20a%20higher%20flow%20rate%20but%20not%20more%20than%206%20to%208%20litres%20per%20minute.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20ideal%20scenario%2C%20no%20tap%20should%20have%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%20more%20than%206%20litres%20a%20minute%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20look%20at%20multiple%20use%20cases%20in%20terms%20of%20hospitals%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20bulk%20washing%20areas%2C%20their%20requirements%20are%20very%20different%20and%20not%20everyone%20can%20live%20with%20spray%20taps%20releasing%203%20litres%20a%20minute.%20We%20started%20looking%20at%20custom%20designs%20and%20solutions.%20Our%20company%20does%20comprehensive%20water%20audits%20for%20businesses%20and%20provides%20solutions%20for%20varied%20sizes%20of%20taps%2C%20addressing%20diverse%20types%20of%20flow%20rates%20that%20are%20required%2C%20and%20implementing%20them%20end-to-end%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAerators%20manufactured%20by%20EverythingECO%20start%20with%20flow%20rates%20(per%20minute)%20of%201%20litre%2C%203%20litres%2C%204%20litres%2C%20and%206%20litres.%20%E2%80%9CAerators%20with%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%200.5%20and%201%20litre%20per%20minute%20usually%20offer%20a%20mist-type%20flow.%20But%20for%20commercial%20and%20residential%20apartments%2C%20this%20flow%20rate%20is%20too%20low%20to%20wash%20hands.%20For%20hand%20wash%20taps%2C%20our%20aerator%20which%20restricts%20flow%20rates%20to%203%20litres%20a%20minute%20is%20popular%20across%20all%20sectors.%20Many%20people%20opt%20for%203%20litres%20a%20minute%20aerator%20for%20their%20kitchen%20taps%20as%20well%2C%20because%20it%20effectively%20covers%20a%20larger%20area%20for%20washing%20utensils.%20If%20customers%20want%20laminar%20flow%20in%20their%20kitchen%20taps%2C%20then%20they%20go%20for%204%20or%206%20litres%20a%20minute%20aerators%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRestrictors%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20that%20is%20coming%20out%20from%20the%20pipes%20or%20the%20entry%20points.%20You%20can%20attach%20these%20restrictors%20to%20older%20type%20taps%2C%20health%20faucets%20and%20shower%20heads%20and%20reduce%20the%20flow%20rate%20to%20anywhere%20between%206%20to%209%20litres%20a%20minute.%20Depending%20on%20the%20water%20pressure%20of%20their%20shower%20heads%2C%20people%20can%20use%20restrictors%20to%20limit%20the%20flow%20rate%20to%206%20to%209%20litres%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_I--BQBbe1Y%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F_I--BQBbe1Y%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashidhara%20notes%20that%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20questions%20residents%20should%20answer%20if%20they%20are%20serious%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345175%2Fhow-to-save-water-at-home-bengaluru-water-crisis-solution-dr-divya-sharma-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereducing%20personal%20water%20consumption%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20What%20is%20my%20daily%20consumption%20and%20where%20do%20I%20use%20my%20water%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20how%20much%20water%20do%20I%20use%20for%20washing%20my%20hands%2C%20bathing%2C%20shaving%2C%20brushing%2C%20washing%20clothes%20and%20utensils%2C%20etc%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Understanding%20why%20I%20use%20X%20amount%20of%20water%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20using%20400%20litres%20of%20water%20a%20day%2C%20do%20I%20need%20this%20much%20to%20live%20well%3F%20%E2%80%9CFundamental%20living%20requires%203%20litres%20of%20drinking%2C%205%20litres%20of%20cooking%20(per%20day)%20and%20the%20rest%20we%20are%20washing%20and%20flushing%20down%20the%20drain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20How%20do%20I%20reduce%20my%20daily%20water%20consumption%20by%2050%25%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20then%20you%20implement%20solutions%20available%20including%20aerators%2C%20restrictors%2C%20and%20using%20low-flush%20toilets.%20Taking%20a%20shorter%20shower%20helps%20save%20water%20compared%20to%20a%2020-minute%20shower.%20Attaching%20a%20restrictor%20with%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%206%20litres%20to%207%20litres%20per%20minute%20to%20an%20existing%20shower%20head%20will%20help%20reduce%20water%20wastage%20by%2050%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20Shashidhara%20believes%20real%20water%20savings%20come%20from%20a%20collective%20effort%20rather%20than%20somebody%20changing%20a%20single%20tap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20also%20have%20to%20adopt%20a%20mechanism%20to%20reduce%20your%20utilisation.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20install%20an%20aerator%20on%20your%20kitchen%20tap%2C%20but%20you%20are%20washing%20utensils%20for%20a%20longer%20period%2C%20then%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20reducing%20water%20consumption.%20You%20may%20end%20up%20consuming%20more%20water%20than%20before.%20You%20need%20to%20be%20cognizant%20of%20how%20you%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20use%20water%20and%20restrict%20the%20amount%20coming%20out%20from%20the%20taps%20and%20shower%20heads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20city%2C%20we%20have%201%20crore%2040%20lakh%20population%2C%20150%20litres%20of%20water%20consumption%20per%20person%20per%20day%20is%20required%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bangalore%20Water%20Supply%20%26amp%3B%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB)%20chairperson%20Dr%20V%20Ram%20Prasath%20Manohar%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fbengaluru-bans-use-of-drinking-water-for-other-purposes-as-water-crisis-rages%2Farticleshow%2F108452077.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20news%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%2013%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurely%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20use%20this%20much%20water%20on%20a%20given%20day%20and%20can%20find%20ways%20to%20save%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-2-1-1-1712314776.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Why%20Bengaluru%20needs%20to%20save%20water%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-2-1-1-1712314776.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-2-1-1-1712314776-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-2-1-1-1712314776-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-2-1-1-1712314776-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-2-1-1-1712314776-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Large%20plastic%20pots%20arranged%20in%20queues%20by%20the%20residents%20to%20collect%20drinking%20water%C2%A0in%20Bengaluru%20in%20March%202024%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStandardisation%20of%20taps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20challenge%20we%20have%20observed%20recently%20is%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20tap%20designs%20are%20changing.%20This%20is%20an%20important%20aspect%20I%20want%20to%20highlight%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20dire%20need%20for%20standardisation%20across%20the%20industry%2C%20builders%2C%20and%20Government%20on%20standardising%20fixtures%20backed%20by%20a%20rating%20system%20for%20water%20conservation%20or%20efficiency.%20Unless%20standardisation%20sets%20in%2C%20new%20tap%20designs%20will%20emerge%20and%20none%20of%20the%20aerators%20will%20be%20compatible.%20When%20that%20happens%2C%20flow%20rates%20return%20to%2016%20litres%2Fminute%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Fgovt-moots-star-rating-system-for-water-taps-sanitary-fixtures%2Farticle66789559.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20Government%20was%20bringing%20in%20a%20star%20rating%20system%20for%20water%20fixtures%20similar%20to%20the%20ratings%20of%20electrical%20appliances.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20rating%20system%20would%20have%203%2C%204%20and%205-star%20water%20fixtures%20based%20on%20their%20water%20efficiency%20and%20this%20rating%20system%20would%20come%20under%20one%20umbrella%20called%20Bharat%20Tap%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20now%20roped%20in%20the%20Indian%20Plumbing%20Association%20and%20all%20manufacturers%20to%20adopt%20and%20promote%20these%20standards%20and%20bring%20in%20water-efficient%20fixtures.%20Bharat%20Tap%20is%20a%20collaborative%20effort%20which%20was%20formulated%20under%20AMRUT%202.0%20to%20drive%20water%20efficiency%2C%20and%20this%20can%20be%20achieved%20only%20if%20water%20outlets%20are%20efficient%2C%20be%20it%20sanitary%20fixtures%20or%20taps%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20D%20Thara%2C%20Additional%20Secretary%2C%20MoHUA%20(Ministry%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs)%20and%20Mission%20Director%2C%20AMRUT%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20this%20report%2C%20however%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20news%20reports%20of%20this%20initiative%E2%80%99s%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20toilet-flushing%20water%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20attaching%20aerators%20and%20restrictors%20in%20your%20home%2C%20another%20step%20you%20can%20take%20is%20to%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20you%20use%20to%20flush%20toilets.%20According%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesoftcopy.in%2F2020%2F01%2F23%2Fbluru-flushing-its-way-to-waterless-apocalypse%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520total%2520population%2520of%2520Bangalore%2Cwater%2520on%2520a%2520daily%2520basis.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20one%20estimate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20city%20is%20flushing%20out%20an%20incredible%20486.5%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20daily.%20People%20can%20install%20a%20low-flush%20toilet%2C%20use%20non-potable%20treated%20water%20instead%20of%20freshwater%2C%20or%20adopt%20hacks%20like%20the%20one%20developed%20by%20Subburaman%20M%20%E2%80%94%20a%20septuagenarian%20and%20resident%20of%20Trichy%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20who%20won%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20improving%20sanitation%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubburaman%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Society%20for%20Community%20Organisation%20and%20People%E2%80%99s%20Education%20(SCOPE)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20which%20has%20installed%201.2%20lakh%20toilets%20across%20India.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20developed%20a%20simple%20solution%20in%20his%20home%20that%20allows%20greywater%20generated%20from%20washing%20hands%20to%20be%20used%20for%20flushing%20the%20toilet%20instead%20of%20fresh%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20422px)%20100vw%2C%20422px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSubburaman-1712575550.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22422%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20you%20can%20save%20water%20in%20Bengaluru%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSubburaman-1712575550.jpg%20422w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSubburaman-1712575550-137x300.jpg%20137w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSubburaman-1712575550-150x327.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346784%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22921%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESubburaman%20using%20the%20washbasin%20fitted%20over%20his%20toilet%20to%20save%20water%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252861%2Fsubbaraman-m-tamil-nadu-ngo-scope-reuse-save-water-covid-19-handwash-guidelines-who-wastage-greywater-sustainable-hacks-innovation-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202021%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20lockdown%20period%2C%20everyone%20started%20washing%20their%20hands%20often%20to%20stay%20safe%20from%20coronavirus.%20However%2C%20many%20did%20not%20think%20about%20saving%20water%20while%20doing%20so.%20Some%20people%20even%20keep%20the%20water%20running%20while%20lathering%20soap%20for%2020%20seconds.%20This%20leads%20to%20massive%20wastage.%20So%20I%20started%20to%20think%20of%20ways%20we%20could%20reuse%20this%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Subburaman%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20Japanese%20toilet%20that%20had%20a%20washbasin%20integrated%20with%20a%20toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Subburaman%20did%20was%20purchase%20a%20new%20wash%20basin%20and%20fit%20it%20right%20on%20top%20of%20a%20Western-style%20toilet.%20However%2C%20he%20says%20that%20an%20old%20one%20can%20be%20removed%20and%20refitted%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20to%20connect%20the%20basin%20to%20the%20toilet%E2%80%99s%20flush%20tank.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20the%20exit%20pipe%20from%20the%20basin%20was%20inserted%20on%20top%20of%20the%20flush%20tank%20through%20a%20hole.%20The%20cutting%20work%20was%20done%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20plumber%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Subburaman.%20Once%20the%20two%20were%20fitted%2C%20they%20were%20sealed%20in%20place%2C%20and%20the%20water%20connection%20was%20directed%20only%20to%20the%20washbasin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20six%20months%20before%20speaking%20to%20The%20Better%20India%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20working%20perfectly%20and%20faced%20no%20damages%20or%20leakages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20even%20offered%20a%20five-step%20manual%20on%20how%20you%20can%20do%20the%20same%20at%20your%20home%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%201%3A%20With%20help%20from%20a%20plumber%2C%20install%20an%20old%2Fnew%20washbasin%20on%20the%20wall%20over%20the%20toilet%E2%80%99s%20flush%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%202%3A%20Create%20a%20hole%2C%20as%20big%20as%20the%20outlet%20pipe%2C%20on%20the%20flush%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%203%3A%20Once%20the%20washbasin%20is%20mounted%2C%20insert%20the%20outlet%20pipe%20into%20the%20flush%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%204%3A%20Direct%20the%20water%20supply%20to%20the%20washbasin%20and%20turn%20off%20the%20valve%20leading%20to%20the%20toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%205%3A%20Open%20the%20tap%20and%20let%20the%20water%20run%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20to%20check%20for%20any%20leakages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20up%20to%20three%20or%20four%20hand%20washes%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20flush%20tank.%20To%20avoid%20touching%20the%20tap%20while%20washing%20hands%2C%20he%20also%20had%20a%20foot%20pedal%20installed%20which%20he%20says%20is%20optional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20517px)%20100vw%2C%20517px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSubburaman-2-1712575701.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22517%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Save%20Water%20in%20Bengaluru%20Today!%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%2