0(%40parsi_dairy_farm)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Parvana%20stood%20her%20sibling%20Zeenia%20(37)%20who%20had%20eyes%20only%20for%20the%20chocolate%20dips%20and%20butter%20cups.%20Now%20a%20brand%20director%20at%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%2C%20Zeenia%20gets%20nostalgic%20as%20she%20reminiscences%20the%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20exciting%E2%80%9D%20festive%20days%20at%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20day%20began%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331134%2Fgujarat-sustainable-startup-reroute-makes-ecofriendly-shoes-from-sugarcane-plastic-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20siblings%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20line%20up%20behind%20the%20counter%2C%20their%20feet%20barely%20touching%20the%20floor.%20Their%20faces%20reflected%20the%20anticipation%20of%20spending%20a%20day%20catering%20to%20customers%2C%20getting%20the%20orders%20right%2C%20counting%20the%20cash%20perfectly%20and%20waving%20the%20customers%20goodbye%20(accompanied%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98Come%20again!%E2%80%99%20that%20they%20had%20been%20taught%20by%20their%20parents).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jar%20filled%20with%20coins%2C%20that%20jingled%20when%20it%20was%20moved%2C%20meant%20a%20successful%20day%20for%20the%20siblings.%20And%20the%20mad%20rush%20of%20these%20occasions%20is%20what%20the%20cousins%20lived%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20chaos%2C%20someone%20would%20spot%20a%20cricket%20bat%20lying%20around.%20Its%20owner%20and%20one%20of%20the%20siblings%20Bakhtyar%20Irani%20(41)%20admits%20it%20was%20always%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20cricketer%20of%20the%20family.%20And%20most%20days%20I%20would%20just%20come%20to%20the%20shop%20because%20there%20was%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20toy%20store%20next%20door%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20buy%20myself%20a%20cricket%20bat!%E2%80%9D%20Forthcoming%20about%20his%20passion%20for%20sports%2C%20Bakhtyar